description: Try our easy to follow Brandy Snap Baskets with Orange Mousse recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Brandy Snap Baskets with Orange Mousse
name: Brandy Snap Baskets with Orange Mousse Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spoon mousse into brandy baskets. Remove skin and pith form extra orange. Cut segments from orange and place a few slices onto each mousse. Serve.
